<collectionCode id="ED3CC3C3F76CB12DB182FEB332C24221" box="[199,251,332,358]" pageId="25" pageNumber="546">TYPE</collectionCode>
MATERIAL: In Sundevall’s original description (1850: 103) and his acquisition journal only a single male is listed. The 
<typeStatus id="5496E5A4F76CB12DB057FE90334E42CB" box="[274,375,367,393]" pageId="25" pageNumber="546">holotype</typeStatus>
, NRM 568781 [6751], is an adult male collected 
<date id="FF937DC6F76CB12DB2DCFE90360A42CB" box="[921,1075,367,393]" pageId="25" pageNumber="546" value="1841-04-14">14 April 1841</date>
at Camperdown (Upper Umlaas River).
</paragraph>
